*Decu* su deca razigrala u dvorištu. (The children played in the yard.)

*Deca* su se igrala u parku. (The children were playing in the park.)

*Deci* je bio potreban odmor. (The children needed a rest.)

*Decu* smo zamolili da počnu da uče. (We asked the children to start studying.)

*Decama* smo dali nagradu za njihov uspeh. (We rewarded the children for their success.)

*Deci* je poklanjamo nove igračke. (We are gifting the children new toys.)